1638.title: Regular Expression Denial of Service
1638.overview: `prismjs` versions before 1.23.0 are vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS) via the prism-asciidoc, prism-rest, prism-tap and prism-eiffel components.

1693.title: Regular Expression Denial of Service
1693.overview: `postcss` from 7.0.0 and before 8.2.10 are vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS) during source map parsing.
